			text="Step 3: Reflection and Next Steps">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Congrats, you made it to the end of the second chapter!">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Chapter takeaways: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Remember, the relationships you have, and continue to build, with community members/groups throughout the ERB process will be instrumental to the implementation of equitable actions. Engage your community throughout the ERB process to ensure you can utilize the relationships to inform the project later on. Keep in mind that communities are all unique - tailor the approach to your community.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Reflection: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Take a minute to think about what you accomplished in this chapter. Reflect upon and discuss the following questions, either individually or with your core team:">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- What went well with you community engagement planning process?">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- What was a challenge in developing your community engagement process? How will you overcome it?">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- Who have you planned to engage that may not have been included in previous planning processes?">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- How will you maintain relationships over the long-term?">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- How have you addressed issue of equity with your engagement plan?">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Next steps: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Now that you've reflected, make any adjustments to your community engagement plan or project plan that may be needed. (Remember, it's okay to make changes!) Next, begin to contact community members and set dates for any engagement sessions you planned.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Now you're ready for the next chapter - Click here to start on Chapter 3: ">
